  "description": [
    "THREE Caillaux in Plea For Trust Control in France WOULD REVIVE BLOC OF LEFT HE TELLS VETS Program Will Cut Figure in Future Politics Leader Special Service PARlSJoseph Caillaux former finance minister and still a member of the Radical party recently de livered a speech to French war vet erans which outlined a new program for a revival of the bloc of the par ties of the left This program will play a prominent role in future French politics In a few words this program may be summed up to demand a govern ment supervision of trusts which are necessary for international agreements a better coordination of industries and an extension of the national economic council by taking in the labor unions and the civil servants Need New Arrangements Caillaux holds that the present political parties no longer corre spond to the decisive economic di visions of modern capitalist socie ties The economic relationships have been changed fundamentally whereas the political parties are still the same that existed a gen eration and more ago These political parties have anti quated programs so that their po litical squabbles are largely pre tense or at least have no effect on the new"
  ],
